{"id":103957,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/美国和苏联，谁应被“永远铭记”？/","date":"2010-09-11T09:41:52Z","modified":"2010-09-11T09:41:52Z","title":"美国和苏联，谁应被“永远铭记”？","content":"<p><p align=\"left\"><span>凤凰卫视</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日《总编辑时间》播出节目“马英九：抗战历史不可遗忘”，主持人</span><span>何亮亮介绍了台湾庆祝民国军人节及抗战胜利</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">65</span><span>周年。马英九出席并致词强调，对日抗战八年可说是民族御侮的圣战，这段历史不能被遗忘。马英九表示，抗战</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>年是中华民族历史上最艰苦光荣的岁月。抗战主要战役如上海、南京、武汉保卫战，以及大家所熟悉的台儿庄大捷等，<strong><span>记录了国军在第一线奋勇抗战的壮烈历史，其中国军与日军激烈会战多达</span></strong></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span></strong><strong><span>次，大型会战</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">1117</span></strong><strong><span>次，其它战斗有</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">38000</span></strong><strong><span>多次，可说是空前惨烈。英勇殉国的将军，少将以上就有</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span></strong><strong><span>多位，民众死亡估计至少在</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span></strong><strong><span>万人，而官兵殉职的有</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">322</span></strong><strong><span>万人。这一段历史不被遗忘，更不允许被篡改。</span></strong></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span> ……</p>\n<p>……</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><strong><span><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span></p>\n<p><span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n</p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p>“要翻墙，<a href=\"http://bieyouyongxin.info\" target=\"_blank\">用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[8800]}